    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scoping per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump within the CPB flow and speed envelope described in REQ-CPB-2024-007. No material weakeners identified.",
